Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要吃點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果那樣我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾也可以吃東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 我現在更想吃飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}氣氛好尷尬
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
