Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從今天開始你要和艾拉一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起住是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們一般規定搭檔的執行者和觀測者一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯 我也是和康孝住在同一個屋簷下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過他平常很少回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉住在我們公司的宿舍裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也搬到那邊去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼時候開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果可以的話就今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}再怎麼說也有點太倉促了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣不會很糟糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}而且那種規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的那個淫蕩的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以外行人真的是糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼 你吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看上去是那樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我能理解你擔心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}默默守護著她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天工作結束之後我帶你去宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}…嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宿舍挺大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI公司全部的部門都有人住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿和塞克在旁邊的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠則在他們的旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我進了艾拉的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天開始…我要在這裡…和艾拉同居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在房間裡的東西請隨意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不需要顧忌我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂…忽然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\c&H484747&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(929,10)\fad(0,150)}總算和香月和好了。\N\N結果又是在照顧醉醺醺的香月時\N\N筋疲力盡然後和好了\N\N嘛不管怎樣也比一直吵架要好\N\N可是香月明明不怎麼會喝酒還喝那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}四月十號天氣晴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天和香月吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她生氣的時候真的非常的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話可嫁不出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日記裡和平時簡直就是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是搞不懂女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等…那不是艾拉的日記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼司會拿著它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 這是個誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才一直反對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這小子圖謀著對艾拉做些下流的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有圖謀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,664,640,710,190,690)}有和女生交往的經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是沒經驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓這樣的你和艾拉同居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一點都不覺得你可以保持理性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿有資格說別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞…塞克？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那句話是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小滿雖然那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我可是支持小司的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}支持？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}YES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以為了將你和艾拉的同居生活變成玫瑰色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來教你秘藏的訣竅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其名曰「幸運色狼大作戰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿出你的筆記 這裡考試會考哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽好了 首先小艾拉洗澡的時候是好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要裝作沒有注意到打開門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣在突然邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發出「呀 討厭」的悲鳴的同時也會臉紅心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這才是戀愛喜劇的王道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠 你在說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你也別在這裡做筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小滿你也太激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之 你要是敢對艾拉做了一點點奇怪的事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看我把你從宿舍裡揍出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要說什麼奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}問題根本就不可能到那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我可是好好的傳授給你作戰方案了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然有點不好意思提回報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次能不能替我拜託小艾拉一點事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能不能讓小艾拉穿這個看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這…難道是自己做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得會很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是小艾拉從來不接受別人的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道失敗了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要裝作沒有注意到打開門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打開門…打開門…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看到 我什麼都沒看到！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被討厭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宿舍生活發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又弄不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 還想要喝的話告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是只有在宿舍裡被完全無視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話 就來鍛鍊肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鍛鍊肌肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要表現出你是一個可靠的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順利的話 她可能就會敞開心扉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此 啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 那個啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然回到房間就不跟我說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 如果有力氣活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儘管告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我擦 剛才好像有很大的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們在鬧什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿說司是個變態哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要用這些體育系的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好的交流才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}無論如何白天有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前些日子是不是被女兒說很噁心然後痛哭流涕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}交流的時間本來就有限
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有似乎有被說「不要把內衣一起洗哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不管多麼的累也要擠出一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽好了 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽我說的就沒有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近會做料理的男人似乎很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 很快就要做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來嚐嚐我的手藝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 雖然我是第一次做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是會按照教程來做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在加上點白蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我昨天叫你不要鬧了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼停下這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停下…冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之…停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 請你不要氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康斯坦斯 如果是你這種時候怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嗎 是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對待女士要表現的紳士一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特別是艾拉經常摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好做一個護花使者不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}踩到那個可能會摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先把那個收拾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼送她一束花怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 占用一點時間可以嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 快逃 這裡交給我解決
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你在亂鬧什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話 為了解開結界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要用和平時不同的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚上好啊 艾拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這身裝扮怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我從繪瑠那裡借過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當世界充滿黑暗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我降臨到這個世界…好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 別太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}降臨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我聽說了你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司還不懂得如何和女性相處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在這告訴你一個珍藏的秘笈怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘笈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要強行推倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是一定要完美地偽裝成事故
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女人就是需要藉口的生物啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要強行推倒她的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的哦…的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你啊 每天晚上都搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和女人一起生活真的是很艱難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒能和艾拉好好相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在私下的場合不管是對誰都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底原因是什麼 完全搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子 可能想保持身為一個機器的狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明天是休息日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要把艾拉帶到外面去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我邀請 她也會被拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和工作的時候一樣的感覺對待她就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒必要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和艾拉應該很合得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和那孩子一起生活6年的我都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿出點自信來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託你了 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不要對艾拉暗送秋波哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天 我想一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天 一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼感覺好輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你明天的時間交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太裝模作樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你不也去上個廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 我想給那些在工作中照顧我們的人道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為要買些禮物 所以想請你陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能邀請到是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是現在要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼要穿制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是沒有私服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家穿的衣服的話是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種的怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微試穿一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來試穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個…就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想送禮物的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉身形很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遇到麻煩事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這位客人 發生什麼事了嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}賠償後原諒我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又拖了司的後腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別在意 衣服就下次再買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 我沒幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前我們在這裡見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時候你是來買什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香草的專賣店啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你經常來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偶爾會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要買點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不送衣服作禮物了 就送香草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以給我推薦一些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要哪種類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就選艾拉你最喜歡的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這和我的興趣無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告訴我那是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我根據那個給你推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個… 那個人不怎麼愛說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家裡經常發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃的也很少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如說我也不知道她到底吃不吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有她好像對喜歡的東西非常執著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是個麻煩的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒…沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 我大致瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H575960&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\fs25\pos(243,373)\frx336\fry26\frz22.522}胡椒薄荷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還戴眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老花眼？！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你 買到好東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能幫上忙就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是遊樂園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要過去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是有好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我有個問題要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明禮物都買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼還要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實 我想感謝的那個人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻煩的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒那麼覺得 沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為成為搭檔的紀念品…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種理由行不行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是搭檔 也只不過是工作上的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別那麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和今天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在個人生活上也和艾拉一起留下很多美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回憶……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是這樣的話 就不能繼續前行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我不是為了能夠在遊樂園裡玩耍 而被製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我來之前 艾拉一直是那樣一個人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是小艾拉從來不接受別人的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是我在遊樂園買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想要的話 等等扔掉也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 對不起 剛才我先回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才是 強行邀請你去 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能幫我用這個泡茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
